  "texts": [
    "The scoring used was a Likert scale from 1 to 4 (not at all / a little / quite a lot / very much so).",
    "In Table 2 we present potential prevention and mitigation actions related to processes in requirements elicitation in multicultural environments, their purpose, and the respective expected benefits.",
    "These need to be carried out to ensure that all teams, and distributed teams in particular, are composed of suitable people with required expertise in diversity awareness.",
    "In Table 3 we propose characteristics that may support openness within distributed online discussion forums.",
    "We divide the open discussion forum entity (from Table 2) into two types, namely, the right to exercise anonymity, and the use of an elected ombudsman (changed to Independent Coach following the validation)."
